snippet.title: Neodori Infinity - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Choose your '80s ride and start the journey!

Neodori Infinity is an high speed road trip inspired by retro arcade classics, with powerful electronic beats and incredible drifts, coming May 24th 2023 to Meta Quest!
Wishlist now! https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/6096953473681995/

This is a VR exclusive, powered up version of Neodori Forever with tons of fixes, upgrades, and greatly improved driving physics, developed by @strobetano in collaboration with Commuter Games.

Visit our website for more informations and updates!
https://commuter.games/neodori-infinity/
